          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1686665890186-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add<strong> </strong>most<strong> </strong>of your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>(save some for later!),<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong>, a<strong> </strong>generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your<strong> cider vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a medium bowl</p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
